'''卡斯帕·彼得·舒梅切爾'''（{{lang-da|'''Kasper Peter Schmeichel'''}}，{{bd|1986年|11月5日|catIdx=Schmeichel ,Kasper}}），是一名[[丹麥|丹麥]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[門將|門將]]，現效力[[英超|英超]]球會[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]以及現役[[丹麥國家足球隊|丹麥國家隊]]成員，是著名守門員[[彼得·舒米高|彼得·舒米高]]的兒子，为了区别二人，外界有时会以“小舒梅切尔”称呼卡斯帕·舒梅切爾。

舒米高的足球生涯也在其父親最後效力的球會—[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]展開的，他在代表曼城處子上陣前，曾被球會外借至[[達寧頓足球會|達寧頓]]、[[貝利足球會|貝利]]和[[褔爾柯克足球會|福爾柯克]]。2007/08球季初，他雖然已穿上一號球衣，但由於[[祖·赫特|祖·赫特]]的出現，使他被外借至[[卡迪夫城足球會|卡迪夫城]]。儘管，他曾表示有興趣留在卡迪夫城，但隨著[[安迪亞斯·伊薩臣|安迪亞斯·伊薩臣]]的離開，使他被球會提早召回。2009年1月，曼城買入愛爾蘭國門[[沙伊·基雲|沙伊·基雲]]後，他的上陣機會可謂寥寥無幾。同年8月，他獲准與前領隊[[斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣|斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣]]所任職的[[諾士郡足球會|諾士郡]]接觸，雖然他只在「喜鵲」效力僅1季，對球會和球員雙方均非常成功，但諾士郡於陷入財困後被迫與舒米高提前解約。他轉投新升[[英冠|英冠]]的[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]，僅一季後，便加盟由[[斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣|斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣]]執教的另一支[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]，作为主力门将随队获得[[2015年至2016年英格蘭足球超級聯賽|2015-2016赛季英超冠军]]。

他曾代表[[丹麥21歲以下國家足球隊|丹麥U21]]上陣過17次。舒米高在2011年5月13日對陣冰島的比賽首次獲得[[丹麥國家足球隊|丹麥國家足球隊]]徵召。<ref name="translate.google.co.uk">{{cite web |url=http://translate.google.co.uk/translate?hl=en&sl=da&u=http://www.sporten.dk/fodbold/olsen-overrasker-udtager-schmeichel&ei=v0XOTZO1AY618QPEwcnbDQ&sa=X&oi=translate&ct=result&resnum=2&sqi=2&ved=0CDMQ7gEwAQ&prev=/search%3Fq%3DMorten%2BOlsen%2Bdenmark%2Bkasper%2Bschmeichel%26hl%3Den%26safe%3Doff%26site%3Dwebhp%26prmd%3Divnso |title=Google Translate |publisher=Translate.google.co.uk |date= |accessdate=25 November 2013 |archive-date=2020-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423021001/http://translate.google.co.uk/translate?hl=en&sl=da&u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sporten.dk%2Ffodbold%2Folsen-overrasker-udtager-schmeichel&ei=v0XOTZO1AY618QPEwcnbDQ&sa=X&oi=translate&ct=result&resnum=2&sqi=2&ved=0CDMQ7gEwAQ&prev=%2Fsearch%3Fq%3DMorten%2BOlsen%2Bdenmark%2Bkasper%2Bschmeichel%26hl%3Den%26safe%3Doff%26site%3Dwebhp%26prmd%3Divnso |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==俱樂部==
===曼城===
舒米高出生在[[哥本哈根|哥本哈根]]，<ref name="Hugman2010-11"/> 2002年9月，他加盟[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]並簽訂長期合約，這包括學校，獎學金以及職業時期。<ref name="Schmeichel's son joins Man City">{{en}}{{cite news |title=Schmeichel's son joins Man City |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/2241867.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=6 September 2002 |accessdate=19 August 2007 }}</ref>2006年1月，他被球會外借至[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]球會[[達寧頓足球會|達寧頓]]，<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Schmeichel joins Quakers on loan |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/4610178.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=13 January 2006 |accessdate=19 August 2007 |archive-date=2006-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060221121925/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/d/darlington/4610178.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>1月14日，他在{{Link-en|達寧頓運動場|The Darlington Arena|96.6 TFM運動場}}對[[彼德堡聯足球會|彼德堡]]的賽事中首次正選上陣，雖然他被{{Link-en|占士·昆尼|James Quinn (footballer)}}攻破大門，球隊最終仍以2-1的比分擊敗對手。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Darlington 2–1 Peterborough |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/4590336.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=14 January 2006 |accessdate=20 June 2007 }}</ref>三天後，他在對[[甘士比足球會|甘士比]]的賽事中首次不失一球。其後，他再代表達寧頓上陣兩次後便重返曼城。

2月，舒米高返回曼城一個月後再度被球會外借加盟[[貝利足球會|貝利]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Bury sign Man City's Schmeichel |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/bury/4736578.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=21 February 2006 |accessdate=19 August 2007 }}</ref>他在三個月的借用期內代表貝利上陣15場賽事。他在下季再度被外借至貝利三個月。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Schmeichel returns to Gigg Lane |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/bury/5279498.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=23 August 2006 |accessdate=19 August 2007 }}</ref>

2007年1月，舒米高被球會外借至[[蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|蘇超]]球會[[福爾柯克足球會|福爾柯克]]，直至2006-07球季結束。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Schmeichel gets Falkirk loan move |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/f/falkirk/6251405.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=11 January 2007 |accessdate=19 August 2007 |archive-date=2007-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070117150413/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/f/falkirk/6251405.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2007年2月18日，他在對[[格拉斯哥流浪足球會|格拉斯哥流浪]]的賽事後獲選為該場賽事最佳球員。5月，他透露原本希望延長借用期，而[[福爾柯克足球會|福爾柯克]]在6月卻表示有興趣買入他。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Schmeichel keen on Falkirk stay |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/f/falkirk/6574929.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=21 May 2007 |accessdate=19 August 2007 |archive-date=2007-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070822204844/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/f/falkirk/6574929.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Falkirk target Schmeichel switch |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/f/falkirk/6224204.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=20 June 2007 |accessdate=19 August 2007 |archive-date=2007-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070707050158/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/f/falkirk/6224204.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[File:Kasper_Schmeichel_2.JPG|thumb]]效力期間]]

8月3日，[[赫斯足球會|赫斯]]稱他們有意買入舒米高。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Hearts admit Schmeichel interest |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/6929382.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2007-08-03 |accessdate=2010-05-28 |archive-date=2020-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423021048/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/6929382.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2007年8月11日，舒米高在對[[韋斯咸足球會|韋斯咸]]的賽事中首次代表曼城上陣。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |first=Chris |last=Bevan |title=West Ham 0–2 Man City |url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6931065.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=11 August 2007 |accessdate=19 August 2007 |archive-date=2020-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423021053/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6931065.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2007年8月19日，他在對童年愛隊[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]的[[曼徹斯特打吡|曼徹斯特打吡]]中上陣，而且保持不失球，使曼城以1-0的比分於主場擊敗對手。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |first=Chris |last=Bevan |title=Man City 1–0 Man Utd |url=http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6941879.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=19 August 2007 |accessdate=19 August 2007 |archive-date=2008-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081014085855/http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6941879.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>2007年8月25日，他在對[[阿仙奴足球會|阿仙奴]]的賽事中撲出[[羅賓·雲佩斯|羅賓·雲佩斯]]主罰的[[十二碼|十二碼]]。儘管如此，曼城仍然以0-1的比分落敗，但他卻獲選為該場賽事最佳球員。2007-08球季，他代表曼城上陣了開季七場賽事，在對陣[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]，[[韋斯咸足球會|韋斯咸]]，[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]以及[[德比郡足球俱樂部|打吡郡]]中不保持不失球，僅失五球。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |title=Kasper Schmeichel |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=37210&season_id=137 |work=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=3 December 2013 |archive-date=2020-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200613094022/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=37210&season_id=137 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
[[File:Kasper_Schmeichel_2006.jpg|thumb]]其間在訓練中作出撲救]]
2007年9月，舒米高與曼城續約四年。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Schmeichel pens new Man City deal |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7009246.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=23 September 2007 |accessdate=23 September 2007 |archive-date=2009-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090526211143/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7009246.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>10月25日，曼城根據協議讓他外借至[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球會[[卡迪夫城足球會|卡迪夫城]]效力一個月。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Cardiff seal Schmeichel loan deal |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/7062022.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=25 October 2007 |accessdate=25 October 2007 }}</ref>。10月27日，他在以1-1逼和[[斯肯索普聯足球會|斯肯索普]]的賽事中首次代表卡迪夫城上陣<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Cardiff 1–1 Scunthorpe |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/7054123.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=27 October 2007 |accessdate=28 October 2007 }}</ref>。

借用期快將結束時，舒米高提出讓他繼續留在卡迪夫城，最終在11月22日獲球會延長其借用期直至到新一年，時任領隊[[斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣|斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣]]說如果曼城沒有傷患的問題的話，他可以留在卡迪夫城整季。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Kasper can stay at Ninian into the new year |url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/kasper-can-stay-ninian-new-2219786 |work=South Wales Echo |publisher=Media Wales |date=22 November 2007 |accessdate=3 December 2013 |archive-date=2020-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423021125/https://www.walesonline.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/kasper-can-stay-ninian-new-2219786 |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，當斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣選擇[[祖·赫特|祖·赫特]]為正選門將後，[[安迪亞斯·伊薩臣|安迪亞斯·伊薩臣]]便提出轉會請求。這意味著斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣並不會容許在明年1月2日借用期便結束的他繼續待在卡迪夫城。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Kasper ready to ghost away from Ninian following Sven's summons |url=http://icwales.icnetwork.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2007/12/22/kasper-ready-to-ghost-away-from-ninian-following-sven-s-summons-91466-20279549/ |work=South Wales Echo |publisher=Media Wales |date=22 December 2007 |accessdate=22 December 2007 |archive-date=2007-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071227164349/http://icwales.icnetwork.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2007/12/22/kasper-ready-to-ghost-away-from-ninian-following-sven-s-summons-91466-20279549/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>同年12月31日，斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣向卡迪夫拋出救生索，就他是否繼續留在{{Link-en|尼尼安公園球場|Ninian Park}}一事展開會談。最終，他獲准再代表卡迪夫城上陣多兩次，前題是安迪亞斯·伊薩臣未能在1月轉會市場末段時離隊。稍後，他表示願意在未來再度效力卡迪夫城。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |first=Terry |last=Phillips |title=Sven's new year gift to Cardiff City |url=http://icwales.icnetwork.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2007/12/31/sven-s-new-year-gift-to-cardiff-city-91466-20299434/ |work=South Wales Echo |publisher=Media Wales |date=31 December 2007 |accessdate=31 November 2007 |archive-date=2008-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080112074930/http://icwales.icnetwork.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2007/12/31/sven-s-new-year-gift-to-cardiff-city-91466-20299434/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news |first=Steve |last=Tucker |title=Schmeichel content to extend Cardiff stay |url=http://icwales.icnetwork.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2008/01/01/schmeichel-content-to-extend-cardiff-stay-91466-20301556/ |work=Western Mail |publisher=Media Wales |date=1 January 2008 |accessdate=2 January 2008 |archive-date=2008-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080501103101/http://icwales.icnetwork.co.uk/footballnation/cardiff-city-fc/2008/01/01/schmeichel-content-to-extend-cardiff-stay-91466-20301556/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>最終，在2008年1月3日，他重返[[曼徹斯特城足球俱樂部|東地球場]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.cardiffcityfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10335~1205866,00.html |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120526210350/http://www.cardiffcityfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10335~1205866,00.html |archivedate=2012-05-26 |title=Kasper returns to Manchester City |publisher=''cardiffcityfc.co.uk'' |date=3 January 2008 |accessdate=3 December 2013 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

3月14日，舒米高被球會外借至[[高雲地利足球會|高雲地利]]直至球季結束。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.ccfc.premiumtv.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10269~1264260,00.html |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120526210351/http://www.ccfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10269~1264260,00.html |archivedate=2012-05-26 |title=Sky Blues agree Schmeichel deal |publisher=''ccfc.co.uk'' |date=13 March 2008 |accessdate=3 December 2013 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 當球季快將結束時，他的父親[[彼得·舒米高|彼得·舒米高]]在一次電視採訪時評論道他的兒子在曼城並不快樂，而且準備在球季結束後離開俱樂部。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Schmeichel set for Man City exit |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/7351151.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2 May 2008 |accessdate=13 August 2008 }}</ref>

儘管希望離隊，舒米高仍然在球季結束後重返曼城並改穿16號球衣。他一再表示希望離開曼城並對簽訂了四年合約感到後悔。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Schmeichel wants City exit |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_3974080,00.html |work=Sky Sports |publisher=BSkyB |date=13 August 2008 |accessdate=13 August 2008 |archive-date=2008-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080918173509/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11679_3974080,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[File:Kasper_Schmeichel_(1240546579).jpg|thumb]]的賽事中]]

11月16日，舒米高在以2-2逼和[[侯城足球會|侯城]]的賽事上半場14分鐘時入替腳踝受傷的祖·赫特。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |first=Paul |last=Fletcher |title=Hull 2–2 Man City |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7715659.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=16 November 2008 |accessdate=15 August 2009 }}</ref>2008年12月，舒米高在[[歐洲足協盃|歐洲足協盃]]對陣[[桑坦德競技|桑坦德競技]]的賽事中為曼城作最後一次上陣。<ref name="thisisnottingham.co.uk">{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.nottinghampost.com/Brave-Schmeichel-deserves-World-Cup-place-says-Backe/story-12207172-detail/story.html |title=Notts County manager Hans Backe believes Kasper Schmeichel has a bright future ahead of him | Nottingham Post |publisher=''Nottingham Post'' |date=13 November 2009 |accessdate=3 December 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208002928/http://www.nottinghampost.com/Brave-Schmeichel-deserves-World-Cup-place-says-Backe/story-12207172-detail/story.html |archivedate=2013年12月8日 }}</ref> 2009年1月4日，他向[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]透露難以競逐正選位置，而他已經準備離開[[曼徹斯特城足球俱樂部|東地球場]]。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Monday's gossip column |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/gossip_and_transfers/7811007.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=5 January 2009 |accessdate=8 February 2009 }}</ref>

===諾士郡===
2009年8月14日，舒米高以據信破球會紀錄的轉會費加盟[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]球會[[諾士郡足球會|諾士郡]]。這則轉會使他與前曼城領隊—時任諾士郡足球總監[[斯文·約蘭·艾歷臣|艾歷臣]]重遇<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Magpies snap up keeper Schmeichel |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/notts_county/8201444.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=14 August 2009 |accessdate=15 August 2009 |archive-date=2013-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601153054/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/notts_county/8201444.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他是球會最高薪的球員，年薪達100萬英鎊<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |title=Saving Notts County |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/simonaustin/2010/03/saving_notts_county.html |accessdate=2010-04-29 |archive-date=2010-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100326030628/http://www.bbc.co.uk/blogs/simonaustin/2010/03/saving_notts_county.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。8月22日，他在以3-0的比分擊敗[[杜根咸足球會|杜根咸]]的賽事中處子上陣並保持不失球。 在2009年9月舒米高的大膽差點幾乎讓他對莫克姆獲得的首個運動戰進球，當他在比賽最後階段走到前場接應角球。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oreKpLxqp60 |title=YouTube |publisher=YouTube |date= |accessdate=3 December 2013 |archive-date=2020-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423021229/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oreKpLxqp60 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

舒米高在10月一連串的表現使他贏得該月最佳球員。<ref>{{en}}{{cite news |url=http://www.nottscountyfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10426~1875493,00.html |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120526210353/http://www.nottscountyfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10426~1875493,00.html |archivedate=2012-05-26 |title=Kasper delighted with award |work=nottscountyfc.co.uk |publisher=Notts County F.C. |date=14 November 2009 |accessdate=3 December 2013 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>舒米高效力綽號「喜鵲」諾士郡期間，球會每2場英乙賽事平均只失0.67球(43場賽事只失29球)。舒米高在諾士郡場均零封對手率為令人震驚的55.8(43場有24場不失球)。<ref>{{cite news  |title=Soccerbase  |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=37210&season_id=139  |accessdate=2016-03-12  |archive-date=2020-06-13  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200613094041/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=37210&season_id=139  |dead-url=no  }}</ref>在4月27日，他在以5-0的比分擊敗早已降班的[[達寧頓足球會|達寧頓]]的賽事後贏得[[2009年至2010年英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]冠軍，以及取得升班[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]的資格<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
| title = League Two - Notts County clinch title
| url = http://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/27042010/58/league-notts-county-clinch-title.html
| publisher = Eurosport
| date = 2010-04-22
| accessdate = 2010-05-28
| archive-date = 2010-05-01
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100501181515/http://uk.eurosport.yahoo.com/27042010/58/league-notts-county-clinch-title.html
| dead-url = no
}}</ref><ref>{{en}}{{cite news
| title = Darlington 0–5 Notts County
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/8621001.stm
| publisher = BBC Sport
| date = 2010-04-27
| accessdate = 2010-05-28
| archive-date = 2020-11-21
